<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.7">
<l>tirivik kiramaṉ centā maraikkaṇem māṉeṉ ceṅkaṉivā</l>
<l>yuruvil polinta veḷḷai paḷiṅkuniṟattaṉa ṉeṉṟeṉ ṟuḷḷip</l>
<l>paravi paṇintu pallūḻi yūḻiniṉ pāta paṅkayamē</l>
<l>maruvi toḻumaṉa mētantāy vallaikāṇeṉ vāmaṉaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who gave the mind that worships, joining</l>
<l>the lotuses [that are] your feet in many, many aeons, humbling itself, revering,</l>
<l>thinking [of you], saying [and] saying “Trivikrama, our lord with red lotus eyes,</l>
<l>my formless, flourishing, white crystal-coloured one with a red fruit mouth,</l>
	<l>you are strong, see, my Vāmana.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
